title: Kim Hyung Jun releases comeback teaser for new song 'Count on You' | allkpop.com
text:

Remember Me Kim Hyung Jun releases comeback teaser for new song 'Count on You' By KpopJoA 17 minutes ago 1,337 202 0 0 Google+ Following a set of teaser images , singer Kim Hyung Jun recently released a teaser hinting at his comeback with mini album 'AM to PM 5-11-3' .
Set in a wintry background neatly aligned with trees, the video is accompanied by slow piano notes when it suddenly kicks off with Kim Hyung Jun singing his new song " "Count on You ". 
The Double S 301 member's third mini album can be heard on March 8.
